      <lom xsi:schemaLocation="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/lomv1.0/lomLoose.xsd" xmlns="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM">

          </identifier>
          <title>
            <string language="en">Chattanooga, Tennessee: Train Town</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Chattanooga, Tennessee: Serie Stadt</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Chattanooga, Tennessee : Ville de Train</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Chattanooga, Tennessee: Cidade Do Trem</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Chattanooga, Tennessee: Città Del Treno</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Σατανούγκα, Tennessee: Πόλη τραίνων</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Chattanooga, Tennessee: Ciudad Del Tren</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">helps students see how geography and promotion combined to encourage the growth of Chattanooga, Tennessee, and how railroads shaped the organization and architecture of this and other cities from the mid-1800s to mid-1990s.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Hilfen Kursteilnehmer sehen, wie Geographie und 
Förderung kombinierten, um das Wachstum von Chattanooga, Tennessee 
anzuregen und wie Eisenbahnen die Organisation und die Architektur von
diesem und von anderen Städte vom mid-1800s zu den Mid-1990s formten.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">les étudiants d'aides voient comment la 
géographie et la promotion ont combiné pour encourager la croissance
de Chattanooga, Tennessee, et comment les chemins de fer ont formé 
l'organisation et l'architecture de ceci et d'autres villes du 
mid-1800s au milieu des années 90.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">os estudantes das ajudas vêem como a geografia e
o promotion combinaram para incentivar o crescimento de Chattanooga, 
Tennessee, e como as estradas de ferro deram forma à organização e 
à arquitetura desta e de outras cidades do mid-1800s aos mid-1990s.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">gli allievi di aiuti vedono come la geografia e 
la promozione hanno unito per consigliare allo sviluppo di 
Chattanooga, Tennessee e come le ferrovie hanno modellato 
l'organizzazione e l'architettura questa e di altre città dal 
mid-1800s ai mid-1990s.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">βοηθά τους σπουδαστές να δουν πώς η 
γεωγραφία και η προώθηση συνδύασαν να ενθαρρύνουν την αύξηση του 
Σατανούγκα, Tennessee, και πώς οι σιδηρόδρομοι διαμόρφωσαν την 
οργάνωση και την αρχιτεκτονική αυτού και άλλων πόλεων από τα 
μέσα της 1800s τα μέσα τησδεκαετίας του '90.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">los estudiantes de las ayudas ven cómo la 
geografía y la promoción combinaron para animar el crecimiento de 
Chattanooga, Tennessee, y cómo los ferrocarriles formaron la 
organización y la configuración de esto y de otras ciudades del 
mid-1800s a los mid-1990s.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sozialwissenschaften</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les Sciences Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>

          </keyword>

          </keyword>
          <keyword>

          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Ciencias Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
